description: From a brick & mortar in W.Hollywood to a neighborhood near you, Rounds Premium Burgers is a fun, new twist on the classic American burger stand. Build your own "round" from the wide selection of toppings available, or choose from signature menu items such as "The Western Devil" and "The California." Rounds offers natural beef, chicken, and homemade turkey and veggie patties, and fresh house cut fries and sweet potato fries.
name: Rounds Burgers Truck
